          "name": "Ilanya`s Room",
          "description": "Ilanya, eldest daughter of Avartis Festa, has a gorgeous view of the grounds in front of the mansion. On a dresser inlaid with mother of pearl sit countless vials and jars filled with cosmetics and perfumes. Off to the side, you see an alcove containing three large, floor-length mirrors, set at an angle to each other. A doorway to the east leads out to a hallway.",
